y/3mu5HED\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3mu5HED&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWPRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=41c0647b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3mu5HED</a><br />\n《頭條日報》：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2WoBlJ6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2WoBlJ6&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWPRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=b2d66077\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2WoBlJ6</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3489356294488073&amp;id=581689778588087&amp;__tn__=%2As%2As-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D3489356294488073%26id%3D581689778588087%26__tn__%3D%252As%252As-R&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWPRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=b6a1fca0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3489356294488073&amp;id=581689778588087&amp;__tn__=%2As%2As-R</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:20:37.000Z","msg":"係為左警隊聲譽而降低罪名，因為可以賴證據不足，香港警察是妨礙司法公正。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:59:29.000Z","msg":"又如何<br />\n<br />\n係妨礙? 班奴隸奈得我地班黑警咩何? (代佢地講埋)"}]}